message.entry: Invalid data type. First and second arguments must be double or single arrays.
Dimension argument must be a positive integer scalar, a vector of unique positive integers, or ''all''.
Weighting scheme must be specified after options.
Matrix or multidimensional array weighting scheme must be the same size as either input array or the difference of the input arrays.
Vector weighting scheme must be the same length as the operating dimension or be the same size as the difference of the input arrays.
Weighting scheme must be a double or single array of real, nonnegative values.
No value given for the weighting scheme.
Invalid option. Option must be ''omitnan'', ''includenan'', ''omitmissing'', or ''includemissing''.
Weighting scheme is only supported when the dimension is a positive integer scalar.
Invalid option. Option must be ''omitnan'', ''includenan'', ''omitmissing'', ''includemissing'', ''omitzero'', or ''includezero''.
